# DJGPP patch for gcc 14.2.0
# This patchfile was created by comparing
#   http://www.delorie.com/pub/djgpp/current/v2gnu/gcc142s.zip
# to the GNU sources at
#   https://ftp.gnu.org/gnu/gcc/gcc-14.2.0/gcc-14.2.0.tar.xz
# and curating the result to exclude patches that change any Linux pathnames
# into /dev/DJDIR since this is not needed for a cross-compiler.
#
